{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01UKWSEpAPRCtzdaQDvV1E7N","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have all the information I need to write the change/migration plan. Let me summarize what I found:\n\n1. **Cluster**: 3-node RabbitMQ cluster (rabbitmq-0, rabbitmq-1, rabbitmq-2), all disk nodes\n2. **Version**: RabbitMQ 3.12.14 on Erlang 25.3.2.15 (release series is OUT OF SUPPORT)\n3. **Image**: `rabbitmq:3.12-management`\n4. **Configuration**: The cluster uses `pause_minority` for partition handling, `min-masters` for queue distribution, has guest loopback disabled, and relies on Kubernetes for peer discovery with AMQP on 5672 and management UI on 15672\n5. **Virtual Hosts**: Two vhosts exist—the default `/` and `/app`\n6. **Users and Permissions**: There's an `admin` user with administrator privileges and an `app-user` with limited access across the vhosts\n\n, with both having full permissions in `/app`\n7. **Queues and Exchanges**: Only `app-queue` exists as a durable classic queue in `/app`, while the `/` vhost is empty; exchanges are just the built-in defaults\n8. **Feature Flags**: All standard flags are enabled including quorum and stream queue support\n\nNow I'm thinking through the migration strategy—the main issue is that 3.12.14 is out of support, so I need to plan an upgrade path to either 3.13.x or 4.0.x.  The key changes involve converting `app-queue` from a classic queue to a quorum queue since mirrored classic queues are being phased out, adding HA policies, reviewing whether `app-user` needs additional tags, and handling the deprecated `queue_master_locator` parameter. Let me draft the migration plan and create the ConfigMap.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":497,"cache_read_input_tokens":34208,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":497},"output_tokens":10,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b74bba5f-9368-4824-b7c5-9f0e8e404c5f","uuid":"b4adb1f6-37ba-42a4-836c-5102745f54a0","request_id":"req_011CcRKq5oi8jHxTQHe1msS4"}
